headline.main: UK New Car Sales Dip in February, Pickup Seen in March-SMMT
headline.print_headline: UK New Car Sales Dip in February, Pickup Seen in March-SMMT

lead_paragraph: British new car registrations fell by an annual 0.3 percent to 83,115 units in February, driven down by weaker demand from individuals and companies, but sales are expected to pick up in March, a car industry body said on Monday.
